{"tid":2116252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[冇病都變有病系列]大批市民到私家醫院取籌進行病毒檢測","createTime":"2020-07-20T04:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T05:35:07.000Z","uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dd92a290ab82ef6b72e3e144b8f1782a9ec356","tid":2116252,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398611&amp;fbclid=IwAR1MT3N_hzyFisPDEfbp6jfADDeqXYGwhxMpr_AylGIu0i9a9z8QqZUDFh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398611%26fbclid%3DIwAR1MT3N_hzyFisPDEfbp6jfADDeqXYGwhxMpr_AylGIu0i9a9z8QqZUDFh4&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b9455b7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398611%26fbclid%3DIwAR1MT3N_hzyFisPDEfbp6jfADDeqXYGwhxMpr_AylGIu0i9a9z8QqZUDFh4&h=e3c52ef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398611&amp;fbclid=IwAR1MT3N_hzyFisPDEfbp6jfADDeqXYGwhxMpr_AylGIu0i9a9z8QqZUDFh4</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】疫情持續，不少市民早上到私家醫院排隊取籌進行病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n在九龍塘的浸會醫院，早上六時許，大約一百名市民在門外等候。不少市民自備膠椅，亦有部分市民一家大細排隊。職員表示為了避免人群聚集，提早派籌。<br />\n<br />\n位於黃竹坑的港怡醫院，門外已經有二、三十人在醫院的等候區排隊。職員為他們登記，市民進入醫院前亦需要量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n在中環的嘉諾撒醫院早上未見人龍，職員表示檢測已經改為網上或電話登記，即使有市民到場排隊，亦會要求他們離開。"},{"pid":"af495638c308e2326d7aaf62007627cd7a051ac1","tid":2116252,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79e99b1de0b2936b0a64cf63a889cc300e55847f","tid":2116252,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"入去吊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國專家批評特區鄭氏何許人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fHzAuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fHzAuS</a>"},{"pid":"17517ac83a13f436d2747f6ae18af5ff2677081e","tid":2116252,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"急住去銀行排隊拎一萬蚊班廢老都係"},{"pid":"7b1e19a6115131850362abfedd9b2e92209abf3f","tid":2116252,"uid":288455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">港共成功取得香港人DNA, 為社會信用制度舖路</span>"},{"pid":"8c115585f1a9de64a4992e1563453fa526341634","tid":2116252,"uid":35342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af495638c308e2326d7aaf62007627cd7a051ac1","tid":2116252,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"而家去中國好似要有陰性證明吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd538f24110b839891d68511d3139f14fe46b2e","tid":2116252,"uid":202466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"無啦啦驗咩呀"},{"pid":"125ff81d73874d34f02a0131a052077284d81432","tid":2116252,"uid":294343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"隻病中左都可以冇病癥，你都冇事，check到有事食一堆藥有乜謂"},{"pid":"c07cd1d058130c370cad4890e75da1c3a19b6983","tid":2116252,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"無病去醫院無病都變有病"},{"pid":"da8908a33db05b50426672df6e1cdbcef8dbe8f1","tid":2116252,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af495638c308e2326d7aaf62007627cd7a051ac1","tid":2116252,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"拎紙返大陸著數者"},{"pid":"45af7c1cf6671108ca91e678843753dd03bce719","tid":2116252,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ed9627c9a5064aaff951f0d02b928c46108cd06","tid":2116252,"uid":121697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"